  "text": "I assume that an entity on either path can decide to choose paths of any time and possibly retrace steps, the path changing being more difficult the farther along he is going. Is this correct? I am wrong. This is incorrect. The further an entity has what you would call polarized, the more easily this entity may change polarity for the more power and awareness the entity will have. Those truly helpless are those who have not consciously chosen, but who repeat patterns without knowledge of the repetition or the meaning of the pattern.",
